These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, cola, iced-tea, fanta
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: thriller, romance, documentary, disaster, fantasy
There are 5 different nationalities: colombian, spanish, russian, indonesian, italian
5 different pets are kept: frog, pony, turtle, guinea-pig, fish
 1. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 4. the person drinking cola is the person drinking cola##1
 5. the owner of the frog is the person watching thriller movies##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the colombian is on the left of the russian##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
11. the person drinking fanta is between the spanish and the person watching fantasy movies##2
12. the indonesian is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
13. the italian is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk        | water | fanta     | cola   | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary     | romance      | disaster | fantasy   | thriller    |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | spanish     | colombian | russian | italian  |
| Pet           | pony | turtle      | fish     | guinea-pig   | frog     |

