.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: video-games, filmmaking, drawing, baking, chess
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: salsa, house, gospel, folk, pop
There are 5 different nationalities: thai, turkish, egyptian, nigerian, british
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, airplane, jet-ski, subway
 1. the person driving the subway is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of pop is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the turkish##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is between the thai and the fan of pop##2
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 8. the egyptian is the fan of folk##1
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of house##1
11. the egyptian is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
12. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | baking | video-games | chess    | filmmaking  | drawing    |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | house       | gospel      | salsa | folk        |
| Nationality   | british   | turkish     | thai    | nigerian  | egyptian     |
| Transport     | airplane    | motorbike | subway | jet-ski | bike |

