.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: fishing, woodworking, card-games, writing, board-games
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, thriller, spy, fantasy, comedy
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: punk, r&b, folk, rock, blues
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: weightlifting, biathlon, snowboarding, soccer, sailing
 1. the person who's hobby is board-games is the fan of r&b##1
 2. the person who's sport is soccer is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching crime movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the fan of folk is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person watching fantasy movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
12. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the fan of blues##1
13. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person watching comedy movies and the person who's hobby is card-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | fishing | board-games     | card-games   | woodworking   | writing |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | thriller | crime | fantasy | spy        |
| Music-Genre   | folk      | r&b      | rock       | blues       | punk       |
| Sport         | biathlon | sailing  | soccer    | weightlifting    | snowboarding        |

