.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: nectarine, pear, banana, eggplant, cabbage
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, video-games, magic-tricks, fishing, gardening
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: classical, disco, country, gospel, r&b
There are 5 different nationalities: malaysian, american, argentine, indian, chinese
 1. the american is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 3. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
 4. the chinese is between the fan of gospel and the person eating eggplant##2
 5. the person eating pear is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 6. the fan of r&b is on the right of the argentine##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person eating banana##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is the fan of disco##1
 9. the fan of r&b is in the middle##1
10. the fan of gospel is the malaysian##1
11. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
12. the malaysian is on the right of the fan of country##1
13. the fan of disco is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | cabbage  | banana     | eggplant   | pear     | nectarine |
| Hobby         | gardening | card-games    | magic-tricks  | fishing | video-games   |
| Music-Genre   | disco        | classical    | r&b     | country     | gospel    |
| Nationality   | american    | argentine | indian | chinese | malaysian   |

