.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, water, sprite, soy-milk
There 5 different types of food: nectarine, grapefruit, cucumber, radish, peas
The people have 5 different jobs:  firefighter, scientist, fisherman, electrician, dressmaker
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: sailing, rugby, handball, cricket, baseball
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the firefighter##1
 2. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person drinking water is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person eating nectarine##2
 5. the person eating peas is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person eating radish##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the scientist##1
 8. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking cola is on the right of the firefighter##1
11. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
12. the electrician is on the left of the firefighter##1
13. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | sprite       | soy-milk       | coffee   | water      | cola    |
| Food       | peas | radish        | nectarine       | cucumber       | grapefruit |
| Job        | dressmaker     | scientist        | electrician | firefighter        | fisherman  |
| Sport      | cricket | handball | sailing      | baseball | rugby  |

