 3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the brazilian##1
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the person watching musical movies and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the canadian##1
 8. the indian is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the brazilian##1
10. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
11. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching musical movies and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
12. the person drinking juice is on the right of the nigerian##1
13. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
