.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-7::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: filmmaking, cooking, rock-climbing, writing, woodworking
There are 5 different nationalities: indian, british, malaysian, polish, canadian
5 different pets are kept: hamster, chinchilla, hedgehog, lizard, turtle
The people use 5 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, trike, jet-ski, bus
 1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 2. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the turtle is the person driving the airplane##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the british##2
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1
 7. the canadian is on the right of the indian##1
 8. the polish is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is the canadian##1
10. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
11. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the indian##1
12. the owner of the hamster is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
13. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
| Hobby         | cooking   | writing | woodworking  | filmmaking | rock-climbing |
| Nationality   | indian | canadian     | british   | malaysian     | polish      |
| Pet           | hamster       | lizard        | chinchilla     | hedgehog      | turtle          |
| Transport     | trike      | bus        | snowmobile | jet-ski | airplane       |

