 3. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
10. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
13. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | milk       | hot-chocolate    | sprite | lemonade  | water        |
| Hobby       | filmmaking | hiking | collecting  | sudoku | singing    |
| Sport       | rowing        | lacrosse   | water-polo  | tennis   | weightlifting |
| Transport   | boat       | jet-ski      | snowmobile      | car | subway  |

